data.description: This spacious home on Idaho St. can accommodate many people comfortably. This home is sturdy and has been well maintained. The daylight basement is half bedrooms(2) and half shop. The shop side has water power and a drain to the septic. There is many built-ins throughout this home and the ceilings are average height upstairs and down. The picture windows in the family room look over the backyard and the creek giving you a sense of in town convenience out of town ambiance. There has been new flooring installed in the livingroom and diningroom the flooring to finish the remainder is on site.
